description.plain: “Get in with Me” is a song by American rapper BossMan Dlow, released on January 18, 2024, as a two-track single along with his song “Piss Me Off”. Considered his breakout hit, it gained traction on the video-sharing platform TikTok and became his first song to chart on the Billboard Hot 100, debuting at number 68.
